OL,5,G1800 Inside the Ambulance
OL,6,     FParamedics treat a pensioner with
OL,7,     Fa head injury and a 2-year-old
OL,8,     Fwho's had a seizure. Elsewhere,
OL,9,     Fcrews treat a man with abdominal
OL,10,     Fpain and take a man with Covid to
OL,11,     Fhospital.
OL,12,G1900 Inside the Ambulance
OL,13,     FThe crews attend a man with an
OL,14,     Funexplained broken leg, a boy with
OL,15,     Fpneumonia and a woman with
OL,16,     Fbreathing problems. They also help
OL,17,     Fa man who has fallen under the
OL,18,     Fwheels of his own car.
