OL,5,G2000 Inside the Operating Theatre
OL,6,     F3-year-old Isaac has an operation
OL,7,     Fon his tongue, Lynette has several
OL,8,     Ftoes straightened and David has
OL,9,     Fbiopsies taken from his prostate.
OL,10,G2100 Inside the Operating Theatre
OL,11,     FNigel has keyhole surgery to
OL,12,     Frepair his hernia - but things go
OL,13,     Fwrong when he's back on the ward.
OL,14,     FCarol has a pin removed from her
OL,15,     Fankle, which was previously
OL,16,     Ffractured.
